git --version - to fetch the version of git

 git config --global user.name "HarshaKhande" - configure github username

 git config --global user.email "hkhande@gmail.com" - configure github email id

git init - initilaize the git repository

git add - add the files from the workding dir to staging area

git add a.txt - this will add names file

git add . - add all the files this will add all the files

git commit -m "First simplilearn commit" - this is used to commit to staging area. the files are tracked from here.

 git remote add origin https://github.com/HarshaKhande/SimplilearnGitProject.git - establishing the coonection with the remote repostitory

git push -u origin main - this is to push the data to remote repo

